Package authenticationpkg

Class AuthUser

java.lang.Object
authenticationpkg.AuthUser
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AuthStaff, AuthStudent
public abstract class AuthUser extends Object implements Serializable
AuthUser is an abstract class that represents the base class of all types of user accounts. It includes attributes: name, userID, password, faculty.
